    "section_custom_mV7Xbr": {
      "type": "section-custom",
      "blocks": {
        "text_bMEHb9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why buy a fence from our Chicagoland fence company? ",
            "text": "<p>When you choose Fenceworks, the best fence company in Chicago, you're investing in more than just a fence—you're securing a promise. Since 1967, Fenceworks has been Chicagoland's top choice for high-quality fences and expert installation. Our fences provide beauty, privacy, and enhanced security for your home. We offer the widest selection of materials and styles, including wood, chain link, aluminum, <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/collections/composite-fences\" title=\"https://theguyon41.com/collections/composite-fences\">composite fences</a>, and PVC/vinyl fences. One of our specialties, the Western Red Cedar fence, is a customer favorite for its timeless look, durability, and ability to withstand Chicago's weather year after year.</p>",
            "align": "center",
            "width": "2/3"
          }
        },
