    "section_image_with_text_HzXDVB": {
      "type": "section-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "image_qx3VBP": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/steps-and-picket-fences.jpg",
            "video": "",
            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "A Short Guide to Codes and Permits in Northbrook",
            "desc": "<p>As a homeowner, you’re responsible for ensuring that your property adheres to all the relevant codes. We appreciate that knowing the right steps can be confusing, and this is where our experience comes in handy. We’ll guide you through the relevant permits, and ensure that your property meets the requirements at every stage. </p><p>For example, you’ll need to send two copies of the plat of survey, alongside the fence application. Does your fence need a permit application? All new installations are likely to need an application, as are replacements that cover more than 25% for each side. </p><p>Make the most of our experience and knowledge, and your worries about permits and codes will be long gone! </p>",
            "horizontal_align": "left",
            "link_title": "Contact Us",
            "link": "https://theguyon41.com/pages/free-estimate",
            "bg_color_block": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "bg_color_content": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
